    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-05-15T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-05-15T00:00:00-05:00" n="292"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d292">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 657.119/476</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The French Ambassador</hi> (<persName
                        corresp="frus1918Supp01v01#p_JJJ1" type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Jusserand</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-05-15">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 15, 1918</hi>.</date>
                        <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received May 18.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">My Dear Mr. Secretary</hi>: I have the honor to acknowledge
                    the receipt of your letter of the 3d instant transmitting a copy of the
                    rationing agreement negotiated between the War Trade Board and the special
                    Norwegian representative, and dated April 30, 1918.</p>
                <p>As mentioned by you, these negotiations have been followed by an authorized
                    representative of the French High Commissioner working in conjunction with the
                    War Trade Board. In answer to your question, I take pleasure in informing you
                    that my Government fully approves the articles of this agreement.</p>
                <p>Believe me [etc.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="frus1918Supp01v01#p_JJJ1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Jusserand</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
